<reference id="api_enumeraterecordingdevices">
    <title><ph keyref="enumerateRecordingDevices"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">Enumerates the audio capture devices.</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
   <keywords>
       <indexterm keyref="enumerateRecordingDevices" />
   </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody><section id="prototype">
        
        <p outputclass="codeblock" conref="../conref/conref_rtc_api.dita#apidef/enumerateRecordingDevices"/>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
   
   <p>This method returns an <xref keyref="IAudioDeviceCollection"/> object that includes all audio capture devices in the system. With the <apiname>IAudioDeviceCollection</apiname> object, the application can enumerate the audio capture devices. The application must call the <xref keyref="IAudioDeviceCollection_release"/> method to release the returned object after using it.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="return_values">
   <title>Returns</title>
   <ul>
       <li>Success: An <xref keyref="IAudioDeviceCollection"/> object including all audio capture devices.</li>
       <li>Failure: <ph keyref="NULL"/>.</li>
   </ul>
        </section></refbody>
</reference>
